issue.body:
The issue for '<' was solved in [#1420](https://github.com/jhy/jsoup/issues/1420) but '>' still not being escaped:

final Document doc = Jsoup.parse("<input class=\"text\" value=\" &gt; data  &lt; \"/>");
        doc.outputSettings().escapeMode(org.jsoup.nodes.Entities.EscapeMode.xhtml);
        System.out.println("Output: " + doc.select("input.text").get(0));

Current Output: `<input class="text" value=" > data  &lt; ">`
Expected Output: `<input class="text" value=" &gt; data  &lt; ">`
